data.description: Beautifully updated 3-bedroom 1.5 bath Tri-level located in Hanover Twp. This home has 2300+ sqft of finished living space. You will love the newly remodeled kitchen featuring custom cabinets, quartz countertops, and new appliances. From the oversized living room, you will have direct access to walkout to the backyard which features an inground pool with waterslide. Newer updates included: HVAC 21', Roof 18', carpet 21', pool pump & filter 22'
